{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Client","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Service_Worker_API\">Service Worker API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client\"><code>Client</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/frameType\"><code>frameType</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/id\"><code>id</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/type\"><code>type</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/url\"><code>url</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/postMessage\"><code>postMessage()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Service Workers API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Cache\"><code>Cache</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CacheStorage\"><code>CacheStorage</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clients\"><code>Clients</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ExtendableEvent\"><code>ExtendableEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FetchEvent\"><code>FetchEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/InstallEvent\"><code>InstallEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/serviceWorker\"><code>Navigator.serviceWorker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/NotificationEvent\"><code>NotificationEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PeriodicSyncEvent\"><code>PeriodicSyncEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PeriodicSyncManager\"><code>PeriodicSyncManager</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorker\"><code>ServiceWorker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerContainer\"><code>ServiceWorkerContainer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>ServiceWorkerGlobalScope</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerRegistration\"><code>ServiceWorkerRegistration</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SyncEvent\"><code>SyncEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SyncManager\"><code>SyncManager</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowClient\"><code>WindowClient</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong><code>Client</code></strong> インターフェイスは、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a> や <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker\"><code>SharedWorker</code></a> などの実行可能なコンテキストを表します。 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a> クライアントは、より具体的な <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowClient\"><code>WindowClient</code></a> によって表されます。 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clients/matchAll\" title=\"Clients.matchAll()\"><code>Clients.matchAll()</code></a> や <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clients/get\" title=\"Clients.get()\"><code>Clients.get()</code></a> などのメソッドから <code>Client</code>/<code>WindowClient</code> オブジェクトを取得できます。</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"メソッド","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"client.postmessage\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/postMessage\"><code>Client.postMessage()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>メッセージをクライアントに送信します。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"プロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"client.id\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/id\"><code>Client.id</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>文字列としてのクライアントの汎用一意識別子。</dd>\n <dt id=\"client.type\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/type\"><code>Client.type</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>文字列としてのクライアントの種類。 <code>\"window\"</code>、<code>\"worker\"</code>、<code>\"sharedworker\"</code> のいずれかです。</dd>\n <dt id=\"client.url\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/url\"><code>Client.url</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>文字列としてのクライアントの URL。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/ServiceWorker/#client\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Service Workers<br><small lang=\"ja\">Client の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Client","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Service_Worker_API/Using_Service_Workers\">Service worker の使用</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://jakearchibald.github.io/isserviceworkerready/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ServiceWorker の準備はできていますか？</a>（英語）</li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\">Promises</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"メソッド","id":"methods"},{"text":"プロパティ","id":"properties"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Client インターフェイスは、Worker や SharedWorker などの実行可能なコンテキストを表します。 Window クライアントは、より具体的な WindowClient によって表されます。 Clients.matchAll() や Clients.get() などのメソッドから Client/WindowClient オブジェクトを取得できます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Client","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Client","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Client","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/client","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/client/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Client","title":"Client"}],"pageTitle":"Client - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}